RELEASE NOTES: 

      I&#039;ve released the patches through v1.5 for my English only version of 
      Two-Worlds,  so here  is one more to  finish what I had started. This, 
      like the others is unwrapped  from its executable form for easy apply 
      to my no-install version.



Install:
      
    Extract TW1.6 HACKED_PATCH.7z DIRECTLY to games folder.
    Choose yes to OVERWRITING any or ALL files when asked. 


    BE SURE YOU HAVE ALREADY APPLIED THE 1.5 UPDATE PATCH.
    BE SURE YOU HAVE ALREADY APPLIED THE 1.5 UPDATE PATCH.



    Razor&#039;s keygen must still be used to activate the game if you havent 
    previously done so.




Now you have v1.6...congrats to you.

Enjoy.
